Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:09.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,那個男人的肉棒靠近優子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:12.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,她想起丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:14.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,不斷反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:18.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,但是那男的卻強迫優子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:24.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,硬是把勃起肉棒塞進她口中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:27.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,又硬又熱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:30.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,跟丈夫的完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:36.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,寫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:55.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,老公原諒我\N像色情小說一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,好像很難
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:04.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,永井瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,總編輯說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:11.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,下一本作品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:15.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,一定要寫人妻外遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:19.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,他還真是強硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:23.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,我以前在他手下幹過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:28.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,好困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,光靠想像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:38.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,不夠真實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,的確是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:43.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:45.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,你不會去外遇吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:50.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能外遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:56.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,真是的，新一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:57.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,你好壞唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:05.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,你可別真跑去外遇唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:10.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,真是的 不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:17.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:20.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,哪位?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:23.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,我是後滕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,我剛好到附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,這給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:36.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,-請進 -謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:58.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,下本新作寫的如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:05.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,有點難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:09.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,外遇?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,你沒外遇過?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,我沒有做過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,你很正經呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,沒想過嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,但是聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:45.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,家庭主婦都妄想過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,會妄想自己外遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:54.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,然後自慰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,別妄想了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:04.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,實際做看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,例如
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,跟我外遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:17.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,你沒有妄想過嗎 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:21.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:29.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,新一打的 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:33.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,老公?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,後滕編輯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:58.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,怎啦?又要晚回家?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:02.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:07.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,他只顧著工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,你也想外遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:15.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,開始大家都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:23.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,是你的偏見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:26.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:30.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,新作要好好寫唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,後滕說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,跟你問好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,小說寫得怎樣 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:05.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,他說會幫忙看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,那你就寫看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:16.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,他挺會照顧人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,後藤他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:26.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,很強硬耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:39.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,他只顧著工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,你也想外遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:46.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,一開始大家都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,是你的偏見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:13.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,總編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,我剛好到附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:20.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,很在意你的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:24.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,抱歉請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,寫得差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,我看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:51.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,我以女主角的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,當開頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,不是這個味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:14.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,該怎麼改?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:19.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,開頭寫得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,文筆也是一流的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,這個內容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:39.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,缺乏真實感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,無法興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,你缺乏性愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,你缺乏的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,是經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:07.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,幹什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:14.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,就說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,你經驗不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:26.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,被丈夫外的人推倒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,很刺激吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,很緊張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,這很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:52.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:02.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:10.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:15.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,誰能冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,很久沒有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:39.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:47.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,好熱唷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:53.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:57.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,這很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:04.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:34.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:49.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,身體有反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,你夠 了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:16.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,感覺怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,害羞嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:35.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,不用害 羞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:47.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,主手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,總編輯不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:14.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:19.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:24.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,總編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:29.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,有覺悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:59.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:07.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,總編輯
