Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:40.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,老公不會誇你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:58.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:14.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,任於
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:20.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:06.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:25.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,不可以
