Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,越來越濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,感覺到了?
